{"tid":1044534,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人覺得自己唔屬於呢個世界","createTime":"2019-03-03T03:36:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-03T15:49:38.000Z","uid":239081,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"e6c18e9374dc1424dcd5aea0ce582447fd93fc8e","tid":1044534,"uid":239081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:36:56.000Z","msg":"當思考成為習慣，會發現世界充滿矛盾反智<br />\n人哋講笑永遠笑唔出<br />\n就算周圍都係人，都係好孤單<br />\n因為無人明白自己<br />\n講埋啲無謂嘢"},{"pid":"6c2307e43824ef79a10ade055f9a79358aefb00e","tid":1044534,"uid":43313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"你係咪今年form2?"},{"pid":"24c79ff7a0d040dbd5a04ad5bb770d9d7dce0fca","tid":1044534,"uid":239081,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"6c2307e43824ef79a10ade055f9a79358aefb00e","tid":1044534,"uid":43313,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:41:01.000Z","msg":"你係咪今年form2?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:50:24.000Z","msg":"中二病（日語：中二病、厨二病），簡稱中二，是源自日本的網路流行語，泛指一種自我認知心態，用以形容一些經常自以為是地活在自己世界或做出自我滿足的特別言行的人，是青春期特有的價值觀的總稱。<br />\n<br />\n我唔係活喺自己世界，係覺得同呢個世界格格不入"},{"pid":"64c32a6a6882ac6c53f6951811dbdfd25a0794ae","tid":1044534,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n32歲都仲覺得好多野曾經發生過<br />\n而現在既自己活係修正過既世界中"},{"pid":"52421adb94b41de304a251c7e7ab3840fdcf731f","tid":1044534,"uid":239081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"64c32a6a6882ac6c53f6951811dbdfd25a0794ae","tid":1044534,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:54:17.000Z","msg":"我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n32歲都仲覺得好多野曾經發生過<br />\n而現在既自己活係修正過既世界中"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-03T03:56:33.000Z","msg":"我唔係講緊平行世界呀"},{"pid":"7aa142a94c8f6e0822cd8bd4c6babb2bff602328","tid":1044534,"uid":7246,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1